Q: Embraer Praetor 500机型的机身长度是多少？
SQL: SELECT aircraft_length FROM aircraft_details WHERE aircraft_model_name = "Embraer Praetor 500" LIMIT 1;
actual_SQL:
SELECT aircraft_length
FROM aircraft_details
WHERE aircraft_model_name = 'Embraer Praetor 500'
LIMIT 50;

Q: Cessna Citation Latitude机型的机身长度是多少？
SQL: SELECT aircraft_length FROM aircraft_details WHERE aircraft_model_name = "Cessna Citation Latitude" LIMIT 1;

       aircraft_length
FROM aircraft_details
WHERE aircraft_model_name IN ('Cessna Citation X',

                              'Cessna Citation V',
                              'Cessna Citation X+')
LIMIT 50;
